Spanish recluta, but that's the name of the people 
there. La recluta? Recluta. Recluta. Everybody

02:18.485 --> 02:19.886
know la recluta. La recluta. That would be...

02:21.267 --> 02:28.493
Jose Mireles. Oh, Jose Mireles? Yeah. Yeah, over 
